- These classes work when the `dark` class is applied to the `<html>` element, but there's no mechanism to toggle it
- No theme context provider, no toggle button, no localStorage persistence

**Files with dark mode classes:**
- `/Users/dhavaldoshi/projects/ai-trials/lifemanagement-app/src/components/shared/CellEditor.jsx` (line 13)
- `/Users/dhavaldoshi/projects/ai-trials/lifemanagement-app/src/components/shared/DataTable.jsx` (multiple lines: 50, 57, 59, 75, 89, 101)

