No theme provider or dark mode setup at the entry point.

### 7. Vite Config
**File:** `/Users/dhavaldoshi/projects/ai-trials/lifemanagement-app/vite.config.js`

Uses `@tailwindcss/vite` plugin (Tailwind v4 integration), which processes the `@import "tailwindcss"` and `@theme` directives in `index.css`.

